flutter upgrade
```
Verify afterward:
```powershell
flutter --version
dart --version
```
Dart version must be >= 3.11.0.

### Step 2: Apply Permanent PATH Fixes
Run one of the permanent PATH fix commands from the section above, then **restart all terminal windows**.

### Step 3: Move the Project Out of C:\WINDOWS (Recommended)
The project is currently at `C:\WINDOWS\myproject`, which is a system-protected directory. This caused the "Access denied" errors during the Fix-Switch phase and will likely cause more permission issues. Recommended:
